<paragraph blockId="12.[189,1399,1783,1951]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<taxonomicName authority="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete, 2017" authorityName="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete" authorityYear="2017" box="[189,412,1783,1809]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Astiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deblockiae" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[189,412,1783,1809]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Astiella deblockiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[418,508,1784,1810]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
resembles 
<taxonomicName authority="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete, 2017" authorityName="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete" authorityYear="2017" box="[637,772,1783,1810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Astiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="desseinii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[637,772,1783,1810]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">A. desseinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[777,868,1784,1810]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete, 2017" authorityName="Groeninckx &amp; Janssens &amp; Smets &amp; Verstraete" authorityYear="2017" box="[922,1046,1783,1810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Astiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="latifolia" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[922,1046,1783,1810]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">A. latifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1052,1143,1784,1810]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
in having tricolporate pollen and numerous ovules per locule, but differs in having a small habit (
<quantity box="[1103,1163,1818,1845]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="cm" value="5.0">5 cm</quantity>
vs 
<quantity box="[1209,1334,1818,1845]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" metricValueMax="2.5" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="cm" value="17.5" valueMax="25.0" valueMin="10.0">10–25 cm</quantity>
tall), very small leaves (
<quantity box="[408,557,1854,1881]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.35" metricValueMax="4.5" metricValueMin="2.2" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="3.35" valueMax="4.5" valueMin="2.2">2.2–4.5 mm</quantity>
vs 3.2–20(–30) mm long), small corolla tubes (
<quantity box="[1127,1275,1854,1881]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.85" metricValueMax="2.2" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="1.85" valueMax="2.2" valueMin="1.5">1.5–2.2 mm</quantity>
vs 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.25" metricValueMax="11.0" metricValueMin="3.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="7.25" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="3.5">3.5–11 mm</quantity>
long), small capsules (
<quantity box="[515,644,1889,1916]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.4" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="1.7" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.4">1.4–2 mm</quantity>
vs 
<quantity box="[689,817,1889,1916]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="4.5" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="3.75" valueMax="4.5" valueMin="3.0">3–4.5 mm</quantity>
long), and dorsiventrally flattened seeds (vs not flattened).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
